pedal-play

1) Installation
2) Pedal Configuration
3) Usage
4) License


------------------------------------------------------------------------
Installation

$ aptitude install python3-vlc
$ install -m 0755 pedal_play.py /usr/local/bin/pedal_play


------------------------------------------------------------------------
Pedal Configuration

Edit your ~/.xbindkeysrc and add the following. You might have to adjust
the key which is emitted by your pedal:

"touch ~/.local/var/pedal_play/play"
  XF86AudioPlay  


------------------------------------------------------------------------
Usage

$ pedal_play some/sound_file.mp3

Hit the pedal to play the sound file. Playback will pause when the pedal
is no longer pressed.


